title: The Senate’s AI Future Is Haunted by the Ghost of Privacy Past
description: The US Congress is trying to tame the rapid rise of artificial intelligence. But senators’ failure to tackle privacy reform is making the task a nightmare.

title: Apps Are Rushing to Add AI. Is Any of It Useful?
description: The AI gold rush has thrust services like ChatGPT into every aspect of our digital lives. That still won’t solve your email problems.

title: Urban Company Lured Women Into the Gig Economy—Then Pushed Them Out
description: Home services platform Urban Company helped Indian women get into the gig economy. Now they say it’s setting impossible targets and then abandoning them.
